PrecisAppointment of MUNIR SHEIKH of Ottawa, Ontario, to be Associate Deputy Minister of Human Resources and Skills Development, to hold office during pleasure; and designation of MUNIR SHEIKH to be Deputy Minister of Labour, to be styled Deputy Minister of Labour and Housing, to hold office during pleasure; effective October 5, 2005.
